These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, mexican, malaysian, chinese, argentine, brazilian, canadian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rowing, lacrosse, soccer, skateboarding, handball, golf, tennis
 1. the indian is between the chinese and the canadian##2
 2. the mexican is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 4. the argentine is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is handball##2
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the chinese##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is soccer##2
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the canadian##1
 9. the argentine is on the left of the brazilian##1
10. the argentine is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
11. the brazilian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | chinese | indian | canadian | mexican    | malaysian | argentine   | brazilian    |
| Sport         | golf  | lacrosse   | skateboarding | rowing | soccer   | tennis | handball |

