.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: radish, peas, mango, raspberry, zucchini, kale, lime
There are 7 different nationalities: egyptian, french, german, british, canadian, argentine, nigerian
1. the argentine is on the far left##1
2. the person eating mango is between the person eating kale and the argentine##2
3. the french is on the right of the egyptian##1
4. the person eating lime is on the right of the german##1
5. the person eating peas is in the middle##1
6. the canadian is on the left of the egyptian##1
7. the nigerian is on the left of the person eating peas##1
8. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the british##1
9. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | zucchini | mango | kale | peas | lime | radish      | raspberry  |
| Nationality   | argentine | british  | nigerian     | german     | canadian  | egyptian | french |

