.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: french, indonesian, nigerian, american, chinese, british, thai
7 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, dog, bird, lizard, horse, snake, ferret
 1. the chinese is on the left of the french##1
 2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 3. the owner of the horse is the thai##1
 4. the nigerian is on the left of the british##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 6. the american is the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the french is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the ferret and the american##2
 9. the french is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
10. the indonesian is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | thai | chinese | french | indonesian   | american | nigerian | british |
| Pet           | horse | snake     | dog     | bird | lizard   | guinea-pig   | ferret    |

