.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, coffee, mirinda, cola, milk, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
There are 7 different nationalities: american, italian, thai, egyptian, canadian, argentine, indonesian
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the thai##1
 2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the canadian##1
 3. the argentine is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the canadian##1
 5. the american is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the egyptian is between the person drinking mirinda and the argentine##2
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is in the middle##1
 8. the egyptian is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is the italian##1
10. the american is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | milk  | cola  | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate      | almond-milk       | coffee |
| Nationality   | canadian | egyptian | argentine | indonesian | american | thai | italian  |

