.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: country, funk, salsa, hip-hop, electronic, d&b, techno
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, bus, tram, scooter, jet-ski, roller, trike
1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the fan of funk##1
3. the person driving the airplane is between the fan of techno and the fan of country##2
4. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the airplane is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the fan of country##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
8. the person driving the bus is the fan of hip-hop##1
9. the fan of electronic is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop      | electronic | country | salsa | techno      | funk      | d&b |
| Transport     | bus | roller | trike       | airplane | tram | jet-ski | scooter |

