.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  software-developer, security-guard, police-officer, chef, electrician, freelancer, accountant
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: water-polo, skiing, weightlifting, sailing, swimming, basketball, ice-hockey
1. the police-officer is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the electrician##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the freelancer is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's sport is swimming and the software-developer##2
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
8. the freelancer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | electrician | software-developer | chef | freelancer | security-guard | police-officer     | accountant |
| Sport   | weightlifting   | sailing    | ice-hockey    | swimming      | skiing  | water-polo | basketball |

