.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice, mirinda, tea, almond-milk, soy-milk, water
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, badminton, soccer, swimming, baseball, skateboarding, handball
 1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is handball##2
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person drinking almond-milk##2
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | sprite | juice    | tea | mirinda   | soy-milk | water    | almond-milk |
| Sport      | swimming | basketball | handball    | badminton | baseball    | soccer | skateboarding  |

