.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, superhero, martial-arts, family, comedy, documentary, mystery
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, roller, snowmobile, scooter, train, ship, van
1. the person watching crime movies is the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is between the person driving the van and the person driving the train##2
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
5. the person driving the boat is in the middle##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
7. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the train##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
9. the person driving the van is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
