.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, soy-milk, juice, sprite, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, reading, card-games, woodworking, skydiving, fishing, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking sprite and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | lemonade       | almond-milk         | sprite         | juice   | soy-milk        | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby      | dancing | card-games | baking | skydiving | reading | fishing | woodworking  |

