7. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

