 4. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
 5. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of country##1
 7. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is the fan of jazz##1
 9. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
10. the fan of indie is the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
