 3. the person drinking pomegranateade is the person eating eggplant##1
 4. the person drinking pomegranateade is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 6. the person eating broccoli is the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating strawberry##1
 8. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking 7up and the person eating broccoli##2
10. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6    |   7    |
