6. the analyst is on the left of the person eating corn##1
7. the security-guard is on the right of the nurse##1
8. the bartender is between the person eating cranberry and the analyst##2
9. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |         5          |        6        |     7      |
| Food   | nectarine | eggplant    | garlic | cranberry | grapes              | lemon      | corn    |
| Job    | lawyer | dressmaker | nurse  | security-guard   | bartender | analyst | social-worker |

 